# Narratoria

A work in progress app for an AI-backed narrative driven storyteller and game master.

## UnifiedInference Library (feature specs)

This repo includes a provider-agnostic .NET library under src/lib/UnifiedInference that unifies inference across OpenAI, Ollama, and Hugging Face.

- Quickstart and examples: [specs/001-unified-inference/quickstart.md](specs/001-unified-inference/quickstart.md)
- Contracts and mapping: [specs/001-unified-inference/contracts/](specs/001-unified-inference/contracts)

Basic usage sketch:

```csharp
var client = UnifiedInference.Factory.InferenceClientFactory.Create(
	openAiClient: new OpenAI.OpenAIClient("api-key"),
	ollamaHttp: new HttpClient(),
	ollamaBaseUrl: "http://localhost:11434",
	huggingFaceHttp: new HttpClient()
);

var text = await client.GenerateTextAsync(
	new UnifiedInference.Abstractions.TextRequest(
		UnifiedInference.Abstractions.InferenceProvider.OpenAI,
		"gpt-4o-mini",
		"Hello world",
		new UnifiedInference.Abstractions.GenerationSettings(Temperature: 0.7)
	)
);
Console.WriteLine(text.Text);
```